<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/26776895">XMind在哪些方面帮到了你？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="2893647" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content">XMind 这款思维导图软件切切实实帮助到了你吗？在哪些方面帮助了你？</div>


</div>
